WEBVTT

00:01.929 --> 00:04.389
- Previously;
- Check me out. I'm Mr. Dad.

00:04.929 --> 00:06.679
I need the blood of Angel's son.

00:07.330 --> 00:09.080
- Got it? How?
- Swiped it.

00:09.730 --> 00:12.640
Things have been slow since
Cordelia and the Groosalugg left.

00:12.730 --> 00:16.350
You've been holed up with all those
prophecies and books. You okay?

00:17.530 --> 00:20.579
That the vampire will devour
his child is certain.

00:21.129 --> 00:23.160
- When will it happen?
- It's already started.

00:23.530 --> 00:25.489
The evil beside you.

00:25.929 --> 00:27.960
Earthquake, fire, blood.

00:34.929 --> 00:37.100
- It's okay.
- Earthquake, fire, blood.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.074
